Jesus displayed His level that day at the cross in its deepest and in its most intimate level.

20:30.066 --> 20:33.394
Folks, listen, He died for you and for me.

20:35.362 --> 20:40.869
This abundant love that he has for us today is the same abundant love that he had for us on that day.

20:41.250 --> 20:46.677
And again, we can't comprehend it, but we trust by it and we try to live our lives by it.

20:48.118 --> 20:48.959
We're dear to him.

20:50.642 --> 20:56.049
We are precious in his sight, little kitty song, Jesus loves the little children.

20:56.930 --> 21:03.378
All the children of the year world, red and yellow, black and white, they are white, precious in his sight.

21:04.258 --> 21:09.246
Jesus loves the little children, all of us of the world.

21:10.888 --> 21:24.248
You and I should strive to know more about this love of Christ who went to the cross for us in a more personal and a more spiritual and a more emotional way deeper than we've ever gone before.

21:25.530 --> 21:33.362
We should desire to know this so that we can pattern our own love and our own lives towards everyone else the way that Jesus did.

21:35.618 --> 21:39.442
what you thankful this morning for the abundant love of God.

21:41.625 --> 21:55.680
Not only should we be thankful for the power of the Holy Spirit, the indwelling of Jesus Christ in our lives and and the abundance of God's love, we should also be full and thankful of the fullness of God.

21:56.601 --> 21:58.423
As Paul is praying here, think of it this way.

22:00.025 --> 22:05.010
The power of the Holy Spirit leads to the indwelling of Christ.

22:06.338 --> 22:11.646
which leads to the abundance of God's love, which will lead to the fullness of God in us.

22:13.829 --> 22:19.197
To have this fullness of God means to be satisfied with God in our lives.

22:19.878 --> 22:20.719
Are you satisfied?

22:23.444 --> 22:26.308
Shouldn't all of us want to be filled up to the brim with God?

22:27.710 --> 22:28.431
I certainly do.

22:28.451 --> 22:30.234
I pray that you do.

22:30.294 --> 22:33.138
What all of us should want

22:33.378 --> 22:37.184
is everything that God is willing to entrust us with.

22:39.467 --> 22:43.193
So how do we going about getting filled this way?

22:44.294 --> 22:45.697
What has to do with our pursuit?

22:47.039 --> 22:48.841
Are we pursuing God?

22:49.622 --> 22:55.631
To be filled with Him means to listen, it means that we must empty ourselves of us.

22:58.536 --> 23:00.018
We pray many times of

