of how we're asking God to make more of him and less of us.

23:04.545 --> 23:07.209
Well, I like that prayer, but we should pray it this way as well.

23:07.489 --> 23:08.891
We should really make it this way.

23:09.172 --> 23:12.256
Lord, make it all of you and none of us.

23:15.782 --> 23:19.447
Ephesians chapter 4, 13 says this.

23:21.090 --> 23:21.851
I like this part.

23:21.871 --> 23:29.202
It says until, everybody say until, until we reach unity in the faith.

23:30.114 --> 23:36.803
