It begins with that word you just repeated until.

23:46.076 --> 23:48.879
Little five letter word, but it's a little much bigger than that.

23:50.962 --> 23:59.634
That word tells me that God loves me so much that he's not going to stop until I'm completely like him.

24:01.314 --> 24:06.963
until we reach the fullness and the unity and the knowledge of the Son of God.

24:08.065 --> 24:09.207
He wants me to mature.

24:09.247 --> 24:16.719
He wants me to reach to retain the whole measure of the fullness of Christ.

24:18.161 --> 24:19.683
Aren't we thankful for Jesus?

24:21.867 --> 24:26.474
Who wants to fill us with his love and to fill us with his goodness and in his mercy?

24:26.634 --> 24:28.437
A mighty God we serve.

24:28.557 --> 24:28.978
Amen?

24:30.722 --> 24:38.092
Finally this morning, we should also be thankful according to Paul in this prayer of the glory of God.

24:39.474 --> 24:40.615
We should be thankful for that.

24:41.256 --> 24:47.584
Verses 20 and 21 tells us now to him who was able to do immeasurably more than all we could ask or imagine.

24:48.766 --> 24:59.560
According to his power, that is it worked within us to him be glory in the church and in Christ Jesus throughout all generations forever and ever.

25:00.261 --> 25:00.722
Amen.

