27:13.390 --> 27:22.844
But whether we think they're big things, whether we think they're small things, God demonstrates His provision in all things.

27:24.808 --> 27:26.450
We should be thankful for the power.

27:27.138 --> 27:28.099
of the Holy Spirit.

27:31.524 --> 27:39.956
We should be thankful for the indwelling of Christ Jesus, for the abundance of God's love, the fullness of God, and for the glory of God.

27:41.478 --> 27:43.981
We should be thankful in all things.

27:44.382 --> 27:47.266
We have owes so much to be thankful for.

27:48.868 --> 27:51.792
Every headbound, every eye closed.

27:55.036 --> 27:56.338
As we close this morning,

27:58.146 --> 28:02.612
