29:26.402 --> 29:28.945
His Holy Spirit to live in you comfortably.

29:31.809 --> 29:34.813
If you haven't asked Him to do that, you can do that right now.

29:34.833 --> 29:41.462
Right now as we speak, Jesus will save you, if you will, but ask.

29:43.545 --> 29:44.386
